  "title": "Infant Care Teacher (PG)",
  "description": "<p>Location: East Region </p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>Provide caring and attentive support to infants, understanding their needs and stages of development.</p><p>Organize fun activities that help children explore and learn from a young age.</p><p>Keep the environment safe, clean, and interesting for infants, supporting their physical and emotional well-being.</p><p>Keep parents informed by sharing regular updates about their child's progress and daily routines.</p><p>Work closely with other team members to create a positive and enriching environment for the children.</p><p>Qualifications (Required):</p><p>Advanced Certificate in Early Years or Higher Certificate in Infant Care. </p><p>Strong understanding of infant development and a passion for working with young children.</p><p>Ability to communicate well with both children and parents.</p><p>Ability to create and maintain a warm and stimulating environment for infants.</p><p>Techskills Career Services (S) Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA)</p><p>What’s app your profile to +65 86701803</p><p>Thank you </p><p>Techskills Career Services (S) Pte Ltd</p><p>EA. R23113418</p><p><br /></p>",
